Description_lang: Whirlwind all nearby targets and for the next $d you will perform a whirlwind attack every $t1 sec.  While under the effects of the Tropical Twister, you can move but cannot perform any other abilities.
AuraDescription_lang: Perform the Tropical Twister, damaging enemies every $t1 sec and flinging bananas in all directions.  No other abilities can be used.
